snippet.title: Brasil Fusion - Announcement Trailer | Nintendo Switch, PS4, PS5, Xbox One/Series S|X and Steam
snippet.description:
Brasil Fusion is a free-to-play third-person shooter set in Brazilian favelas, where players must compete online against others in various popular game modes to prove themselves as the best in the neighborhood. Brasil Fusion is coming soon to consoles and PC.

#QUByteConnect2023
